%h2 Orders history

%table.table.table-striped.table-hover
  %tr
    %th Status
    %th Finalized at
    %th Delivered at
    %th

  - @orders.each do |order|
    %tr
      %td
        .label{ class: order.label_class }= order.status
      %td= order.finalized_at.try(:strftime, "%d-%m-%Y %H:%M")
      %td= order.delivered_at.try(:strftime, "%d-%m-%Y %H:%M")
      %td= link_to 'Show', food_order_path(order), class: "btn btn-default"